    "chapter": {
        "bookTitle": "Psalms",
        "delineation": "Chapter",
        "number": 97,
        "summary": "The Lord reigns in millennial glory\u2014The hills melt at His presence\u2014Those who love the Lord hate evil.",
        "chapterAugmentations": [],
        "verses": [
            {
                "text": "The Lord reigneth; let the earth rejoice; let the multitude of isles be glad thereof.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "1\u00a0Chr. 16:31.",
                        "start": 9,
                        "end": 17
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 77,
                        "end": 85
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Clouds and darkness are round about him: righteousness and judgment are the habitation of his throne.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "1\u00a0Kgs. 8:12.",
                        "start": 11,
                        "end": 19
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 20,
                        "end": 23
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 68,
                        "end": 71
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "A fire goeth before him, and burneth up his enemies round about.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "His lightnings enlightened the world: the earth saw, and trembled.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ps. 77:18.",
                        "start": 15,
                        "end": 26
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "The hills melted like wax at the presence of the Lord, at the presence of the Lord of the whole earth.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Judg. 5:5; Nahum 1:5.",
                        "start": 10,
                        "end": 16
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ps. 68:2; Micah 1:4.",
                        "start": 22,
                        "end": 25
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "The heavens declare his righteousness, and all the people see his glory.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ps. 50:6.",
                        "start": 12,
                        "end": 19
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ps. 4:1.",
                        "start": 24,
                        "end": 37
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Confounded be all they that serve graven images, that boast themselves of idols: worship him, all ye gods.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Jacob 7:8 (6\u201315).",
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 10
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 20:4.",
                        "start": 41,
                        "end": 47
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 98,
                        "end": 100
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Zion heard, and was glad; and the daughters of Judah rejoiced because of thy judgments, O Lord.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ps. 48:11.",
                        "start": 34,
                        "end": 43
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "For thou, Lord, art high above all the earth: thou art exalted far above all gods.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ps. 83:18.",
                        "start": 20,
                        "end": 24
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 16,
                        "end": 19
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Ye that love the Lord, hate evil: he preserveth the souls of his saints; he delivereth them out of the hand of the wicked.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Hate.",
                        "start": 23,
                        "end": 27
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Evil.",
                        "start": 28,
                        "end": 32
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ps. 121:7; 145:20 (1\u201321); 1\u00a0Ne. 17:35 (33\u201335); D&C 82:10 (8\u201310).",
                        "start": 37,
                        "end": 47
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Light is sown for the righteous, and gladness for the upright in heart.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "D&C 50:24.",
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 5
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Rejoice in the Lord, ye righteous; and give thanks at the remembrance of his holiness.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Joy.",
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 7
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "D&C 59:21.",
                        "start": 44,
                        "end": 50
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            }
        ]
    }
}